<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?mso-infoPathSolution PIVersion="1.0.0.0" href="file:///C:\ProgramData\Carisbrooke%20Shipping%20Ltd\ISM%20Dashboard\Repository\Forms\Technical%20and%20Safety\RAF%20-%20Risk%20Assessment%20Form%20v2.xsn" name="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:infopath:RAF---Risk-Assessment-Form:-myXSD-2010-09-08T18-23-10" solutionVersion="6.0.0.0" productVersion="14.0.0" ?><?mso-application progid="InfoPath.Document" versionProgid="InfoPath.Document.2"?><my:Main my:DateCreated="" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:od="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:officedata" xmlns:my="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/infopath/2003/myXSD/2010-09-08T18:23:10" xmlns:xd="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/infopath/2003" xml:lang="en-gb"><my:Details><my:Number>D 18</my:Number><my:Title>Embarkation and Disembarkation of Pilot</my:Title></my:Details><my:Hazards><my:Hazard my:HazardId="1"><my:Description>Unsafe rigging of pilot ladder</my:Description><my:Severity>3</my:Severity><my:Likelihood>2</my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures>a) Use of suitable and appropriate PPE: overalls, safety shoes, hard hat, gloves, inflatable lifejacket, etc.; 
b) All crew involved have the necessary training and full understanding of the requirements; 
c) The crew should check the condition of the ladder before it is rigged; 
d) Ensure the ladder is secured to the ship; 
e) The crew should not be required to leave the protection of the vessel's safety rails or bulwarks - A life line or safety harness should be worn if there is any risk of falling. 
f) A life-buoy with self-igniting light and heaving line are to be placed and readily available at the embarkation / disembarkation point.</my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="2"><my:Description>Weather</my:Description><my:Severity>3</my:Severity><my:Likelihood>3</my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor>5</my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures>a) The vessel's course and speed are to be adjusted accordingly to minimise the effect of the weather conditions to allow safe boarding; 
b) If the adverse weather conditions persist the embarkation / disembarkation of the pilot should be suspended.</my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="3"><my:Description>Slip and trips</my:Description><my:Severity>2</my:Severity><my:Likelihood>3</my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures>a) Adequate lighting to be provided. Use portable lighting if required; 
b) Trip hazards and any overhead obstructions to be clearly marked; 
c) The deck area and walkway are clear of any obstructions, cargo debris, etc.; 
d) Ensure the pilot is escorted to and from the pilot boarding position.</my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity>2</my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor>1</my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="4"><my:Description>Communication</my:Description><my:Severity>3</my:Severity><my:Likelihood>3</my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor>5</my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures>a) All crew involved to be briefed prior to pilot embarkation / disembarkation; 
b) VHF radio check prior to the task; 
c) The OOW must maintain continuous communication with the bridge via VHF; 
d) Use of the English language in clear and concise orders.</my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="5"><my:Description>Equipment failure</my:Description><my:Severity>3</my:Severity><my:Likelihood>2</my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures>a) Maintenance is carried out in accordance with SOLAS Chapter V; 
b) The pilot ladder should be inspected and condition checked prior to every use; 
c) A ladder found in poor condition or damaged must be removed immediately; 
d) An additional ladder must be readily available; 
e) When not in use, the pilot ladder should be stored accordingly, protected from the elements.</my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="6"><my:Description></my:Description><my:Severity xsi:nil="true"></my:Severity><my:Likelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor></my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures></my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="7"><my:Description></my:Description><my:Severity xsi:nil="true"></my:Severity><my:Likelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor></my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures></my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="8"><my:Description></my:Description><my:Severity xsi:nil="true"></my:Severity><my:Likelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor></my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures></my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="9"><my:Description></my:Description><my:Severity xsi:nil="true"></my:Severity><my:Likelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor></my:RiskFactor><my:ControlMeasures></my:ControlMeasures><my:ReducedSeverity xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedSeverity><my:ReducedLikelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:ReducedLikelihood><my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:ReducedRiskFactor></my:Hazard><my:Hazard my:HazardId="10"><my:Description></my:Description><my:Severity xsi:nil="true"></my:Severity><my:Likelihood xsi:nil="true"></my:Likelihood><my:RiskFactor></